443
00:22:21,291 --> 00:22:23,791
- ZERO, I THINK
I NEED TO TALK TO YOU.

444
00:22:23,875 --> 00:22:26,416
- ( all gasp )
- ( laughing )

445
00:22:26,500 --> 00:22:28,625
- WHAT ARE YOU LAUGHING AT?
- NOTHING.

446
00:22:30,791 --> 00:22:33,250
- YOU'RE REALLY GONNA BE
IN SOME HOT WATER LATER, ZERO.

447
00:22:33,333 --> 00:22:35,166
- I'LL PUT YOU IN HOT WATER.

448
00:22:35,250 --> 00:22:38,583
- ( both laughing )

449
00:22:40,958 --> 00:22:42,333
- Nina: I'M HOME!

450
00:22:42,416 --> 00:22:45,208
- GOOD TO SEE YOU HOME, NINA.
- AH!

451
00:22:45,291 --> 00:22:46,916
I THOUGHT I TOLD YOU GUYS
TO NEVER ENTER MY ROOM

452
00:22:47,000 --> 00:22:48,250
WITHOUT PERMISSION.

453
00:22:48,333 --> 00:22:50,125
IS THERE ANY REASON
WHY YOU CAN'T RESPECT THAT?

454
00:22:50,208 --> 00:22:52,166
- OH, WELL STARTING TODAY
WE DECIDED

455
00:22:52,250 --> 00:22:53,375
THAT WE SHOULD
LIVE HERE WITH YOU.

456
00:22:53,458 --> 00:22:54,958
- SAY WHAT?

457
00:22:55,041 --> 00:22:58,791
- HA, HA. LOOK, I EXTENDED THIS
CLOSET WITH SOME MAGICAL SPACE

458
00:22:58,875 --> 00:23:01,458
AND MADE A ROOM
FOR ZERO AND ME. SEE?

459
00:23:01,541 --> 00:23:03,791
NOW YOU'LL NEVER EVEN KNOW
THAT WE'RE AROUND.

460
00:23:03,875 --> 00:23:05,791
- BUT WHY?

461
00:23:05,875 --> 00:23:08,291
- BECAUSE WE WANT TO STAY
AS CLOSE TO YOU AS POSSIBLE.

462
00:23:08,375 --> 00:23:10,791
THAT WAY WE'LL ALWAYS BE HERE
TO PROTECT YOU.

463
00:23:10,875 --> 00:23:12,750
- IT'S GREAT.

464
00:23:12,833 --> 00:23:14,791
IT'LL BE JUST LIKE WE'RE
NEIGHBORS WHO SHARE A WALL.

465
00:23:14,875 --> 00:23:16,375
- WE'LL TRY TO STAY
OUT OF YOUR WAY,

466
00:23:16,458 --> 00:23:18,250
BUT HAVING US AROUND
COULD BE PRETTY HANDY TOO.

467
00:23:18,333 --> 00:23:20,208
- WE'LL BE HERE
WHEN YOU NEED US.

468
00:23:20,291 --> 00:23:22,166
SO DON'T WORRY.

469
00:23:22,250 --> 00:23:24,416
- Ichii:
WELL, WHAT DO YOU THINK?

470
00:23:24,500 --> 00:23:26,833
OH, AND IT'S OKAY, WE TOOK ALL
YOUR CLOTHES OUT OF THE CLOSET

471
00:23:26,916 --> 00:23:28,750
AND PUT THEM
IN THAT ROOM OVER THERE.

472
00:23:28,833 --> 00:23:31,458
- THIS IS MY NIGHTMARE!

473
00:23:31,541 --> 00:23:33,666
I CAN'T BELIEVE
THIS IS HAPPENING.

474
00:23:33,750 --> 00:23:36,333
HOW COULD MY LIFE
GET ANY WORSE?

475
00:23:36,416 --> 00:23:38,208
- Ichii: YOU HAVE NOTHING
TO WORRY ABOUT.

476
00:23:38,291 --> 00:23:40,333
WE'LL KEEP
THE CLOSET DOOR CLOSED.

477
00:23:40,416 --> 00:23:43,750
- AH!
THAT'S NOT THE ISSUE.

478
00:23:43,833 --> 00:23:46,291
( crying )

479
00:25:18,375 --> 00:25:20,458
MY NAME IS NINA YAMADA.

480
00:25:20,541 --> 00:25:22,958
I'M JUST AN ORDINARY,
AVERAGE STUDENT,

481
00:25:23,041 --> 00:25:25,541
SO WHY DO I HAVE TO DEAL WITH
THIS EVEN WHEN I'M AT SCHOOL?

482
00:25:25,625 --> 00:25:27,500
- Zero: HEY, NINA,
WHERE ARE YOU?

483
00:25:27,583 --> 00:25:30,291
- Ichii: THAT'S STRANGE.
I CAN'T FIND HER ANYWHERE.

484
00:25:30,375 --> 00:25:35,208
- Zero: ICHII,
THERE'S A BABY OVER HERE.

485
00:25:35,291 --> 00:25:37,083
- THAT'S A GOOD BABY.
DON'T CRY, OKAY?

486
00:25:37,166 --> 00:25:38,625
- ( crying )

487
00:25:38,708 --> 00:25:41,583
- Nina: NEXT TIME
ON "SAVE ME, LOLLIPOP"...

